claim.claim-text:
9. A method for discharging dried product from a container for treating and containing a dried product provided with a discharging system comprising a discharge hole, a pneumatic circuit in fluid communication with the discharge hole, an agitator provided on said container, and a discharge valve interposed on said pneumatic circuit to control fluid flow through the discharge valve, comprising the steps of: 
stirring the dried product by way of said agitator; 
producing a fluid circulation in the container towards and in output from the discharge hole and through the pneumatic circuit; 
performing a conveyance of said dried product by way of said fluid circulation from the container in said pneumatic circuit; and 
collecting the conveyed dried product.
